OL,3,CCould there be a coalition in Coventry?
OL,5,FSince 2010, Coventry City Council has
OL,6,Fbeen run Labour, with the previous
OL,7,Felection giving them 39 seats out of a
OL,8,Fpossible 54. This strong majority made
OL,9,Fit easy for them to pass their policy.
OL,11,FHowever, last night's results have
OL,12,Freduced their power significantly.
OL,13,FWhilst they are still the biggest
OL,14,Fparty, they only have 24 seats. This
OL,15,Fis four short of a majority.
OL,17,FThese are the final results:
OL,19,FLabour - 24 seats
OL,21,FReform UK - 20 seats
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
