OL,3,CCould there be a coalition in Coventry?
OL,5,FConservatives - 6 seats
OL,7,FGreens - 4 seats
OL,9,FThe numbers make it highly likely that
OL,10,Fcoalition talks will take place this
OL,11,Fweekend and next week between Labour
OL,12,Fand The Green Party. If they agreed to
OL,13,Fwork together then they would have the
OL,14,F28 seats needed to make up a majority.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
