OL,3,CCould there be a coalition in Coventry?
OL,5,FRegardless of whether or not they do
OL,6,Fthey, the strong vote for Reform makes
OL,7,Fit clear that they have large support
OL,8,Fin the city. With a third of
OL,9,FCouncillors up for election in just a
OL,10,Fyear's time, and the vote between
OL,11,FReform and Labour so close, things
OL,12,Fcould change again in 2027.
